						               													<description>Goetia the Card Game is a quick, easy to play game for 2-4 players where the aim of the game is to be victorious in pitting the Ars Goetia Demons against one another in a battle of wills as well as brawn.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Will you be able to strategically thrust your Demons into the fray at the most opportune moment when they're at their most powerful? Or risk summoning them early when they're weaker in case you lose control of them and are forced to use them? And will you have the Seals at hand to make sure your Demons are boosted, or enable you to banish your opponent's Demons that threaten your victory? Luck will certainly play a big part when largely uncontrollable entities are involved, but Demonic victory will depend on how well you play the hand you're dealt.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;On a turn each player will play cards &amp;amp; also metal tokens (seals).&amp;#10;It's played over 3-6 rounds (depending on number of players).&amp;#10;The player with the highest points score at the end of the rounds wins.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
